Select ALERTS > Email setup.

Note: Because alarms and alerts are independent systems, the email setup used for alarm and AutoSupport notifications is not used for alert notifications. However, you can use the same mail server for all notifications. Set up email notifications for alerts

Select CONFIGURATION > Monitoring > SNMP agent.

Use SNMP monitoring

1. Select ALERTS > Email setup.

2. In the Recipients section, enter an email address for each email list or person who should receive an email when an alert occurs.

